href=\"/wiki/Ya\" title=\"Ya\">Ya</a></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"width:50%;margin:auto;border:solid 3px #32CD32;background-color:#00FF00;text-align:center;clear:both\">\n<p><b>NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！</b><br />\n<a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN\" title=\"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\">了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"languages\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/Ya\" title=\"Ya\">English</a></b>\n<p><span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"zh-CN\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">中文（中国大陆）‎</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-cyan\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Bamboo_arrow.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bamboo arrow.png\" src=\"/images/d/de/Bamboo_arrow.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>矢\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td>竹箭\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（小型）\n</th>\n<td>1d7\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（大型）\n</th>\n<td>1d7\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>命中修正\n</th>\n<td>+1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>武器技能类别\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/%E5%BC%93\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"弓\">弓</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>规格\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8D%95%E6%89%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"单手 (page does not exist)\">单手</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>4 <a href=\"/wiki/Zm/zh-CN\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Zm/zh-CN\">zm</a><br />（+10/正数附魔等级）\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">1</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>材料\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%91%E5%B1%9E&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"金属 (page does not exist)\">金属</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>矢</b>（ya）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%8F%91%E5%B0%84%E7%89%A9\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"发射物\">发射物</a>类<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"武器\">武器</a>。它是一种<a href=\"/wiki/Category:Arrows/zh-CN\" title=\"Category:Arrows/zh-CN\">箭</a>类武器，专用于<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%BC%93\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"弓\">弓</a>。矢的箭头由<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%91%E5%B1%9E&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"金属 (page does not exist)\">金属</a>制成，未<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鉴定 (page does not exist)\">鉴定</a>时，其外观为<b>竹箭</b>（bamboo arrow）。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#.E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">起源</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">百科文本</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p>矢在随机生成武器中占1.5%。\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%AD%A6%E5%A3%AB&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"武士 (page does not exist)\">武士</a>在游戏开始时会获得26&#xff5e;45支矢。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<p>武士职业的角色使用<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%92%8C%E5%BC%93\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"和弓\">和弓</a>发射矢时会获得+1命中、伤害和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%8D%E5%B0%84%E5%87%BB&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"多重射击 (page does not exist)\">多重射击</a>加成。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>矢是游戏中最强的箭（对所有怪物的伤害都是1d7，且有+1<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%91%BD%E4%B8%AD&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"命中 (page does not exist)\">命中</a>修正），且其材料使得它免疫一切<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E4%BE%B5%E8%9A%80%E6%8D%9F%E4%BC%A4&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"侵蚀损伤 (page does not exist)\">侵蚀损伤</a>，因此是大多数使用弓的角色的最优选。不过，对于武士以外的角色而言，<a href=\"/wiki/%E7%B2%BE%E7%81%B5%E7%AE%AD\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"精灵箭\">精灵箭</a>也是不错的箭，它更容易获得，而且和矢的强度差距并不大。矢和多数远程弹药一样会损坏，因此要长期使用的话，需要收集足够多的量，做祝福处理，并将角色<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B9%B8%E8%BF%90%E5%80%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"幸运值 (page does not exist)\">幸运值</a>提升至最大并携带<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B9%B8%E8%BF%90%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"幸运物品 (page does not exist)\">幸运物品</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>矢最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.1.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.1.0\">NetHack 3.1.0</a>加入游戏。在此之前，武士在游戏开始时会获得一堆<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%89%8B%E9%87%8C%E5%89%91\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"手里剑\">手里剑</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"起源\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\">起源</span></h2>\n<div class=\"noprint sidebox\">\n<div style=\"float: left;\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"维基百科\"><img alt=\"维基百科\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png/50px-Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 60px;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/zh:Main_Page\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:zh:Main Page\">维基百科</a>相关条目：\n<div style=\"margin-left: 10px;\"><i><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ya_(arrow)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Ya (arrow)\">Ya (arrow)</a></b></i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>矢在现实中是指日本的弓箭手使用的箭。矢长85&#xff5e;110厘米，和大多数“标准”的箭（75&#xff5e;90厘米）不同，其长度是专为尺寸较大的和弓设计的。矢的命中加成可能来自其<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bodkin_point\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Bodkin point\">博德金箭头</a>。这是中世纪时期一种常见的，适合于破甲（特别是<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%94%81%E5%AD%90%E7%94%B2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"锁子甲\">锁子甲</a>或<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%94%81%E7%8E%AF%E7%94%B2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"锁环甲\">锁环甲</a>）的箭头。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"百科文本\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\">百科文本</span></h2><div class=\"nhencyclopedia\">\n<div class=\"poem\">\n<p>The arrow of choice of the samurai, ya are made of very straight bamboo, and are tipped with hardened steel.<br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:right\"> </div>\n</div></div>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/wiki/Source:NetHack_3.0.0/u_init.c#line200\" title=\"Source:NetHack 3.0.0/u init.c\">u_init.c<span></span> in NetHack 3.0.0, line 200</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926191424\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.034 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.045 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 400/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2430/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3917/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 728/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 513/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   30.384      1 -total\n 21.03%    6.391      1 Template:Languages\n 17.57%    5.337      1 Template:Weapon/zh-CN\n 15.29%    4.645      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 14.98%    4.550      1 Template:Refsrc\n 14.91%    4.530      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 10.91%    3.315      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n  8.96%    2.723      1 Template:Encyclopedia\n  8.09%    2.458      1 Template:Metal_color\n  7.75%    2.354      1 Template:Wikipedia/zh-CN\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:39667-0!canonical and timestamp 2